 beauty of the historical buildings!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-568x810.jpg\" alt=\"kandy sri lanka transport\"><\/noscript><img width=\"237\" height=\"338\" alt=\"kandy sri lanka transport\" class=\"wp-image-17249 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-568x810.jpg 568w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-300x428.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-600x855.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-237x338.jpg 237w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-421x600.jpg 421w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-114x163.jpg 114w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-126x180.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-539x768.jpg 539w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-718x1024.jpg 718w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130652\/kandy-sri-lanka-transport-758x1080.jpg 758w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\