:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23124752\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23124752\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Great Things To Do in Kandy, Sri Lanka\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>One of the best ways to experience this natural phenomenon is by hiking to the top at sunrise. For this reason, it is recommended to spend the previous night nearby in <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Sigiriya (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sigiriya-lion-rock\/\" target=\"_blank\">Sigiriya<\/a> or Habarana.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tour-kandy-sigiriya\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Book your tour easily online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124907\/Kandy-day-trip-Sigiriya.jpg\" alt=\"Kandy day trip Sigiriya\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Kandy day trip Sigiriya\" class=\"wp-image-18576 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width