tion, which they use to harvest fresh produce for their on-site restaurant. Their true Sri Lanka dining experience is, without a doubt, one of the best Sri Lankan meals you will have.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/aarunya-resort-kandy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Book an unforgettable stay at Aarunya (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book an unforgettable stay at Aarunya<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124911\/sri-lanka-kandy-Aarunya-Resort.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka kandy Aarunya Resort\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka kandy Aarunya Resort\" class=\"wp-image-18575 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124911\/sri-lanka-kandy-Aarunya-Resort.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124911\/sri-lanka-kandy-Aarunya-Resort-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124911\/sri-lanka-kandy-Aarunya-Resort-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124911\/sri-lanka-kandy-Aarunya-Resort-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124911\/sri-lank