nsidered the heart and soul of the city because of its central location and undeniable beauty. In the middle of the lake is a tiny island with a few palm trees, recognized as one of Kandy&#x2019;s iconic scenes, and featured on many a postcard.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Stay nearby:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/kandy-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"See all hotels to stay in (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">See all hotels in Kandy<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130648\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-lake.jpg\" alt=\"things to do kandy sri lanka lake\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"303\" alt=\"things to do kandy sri lanka lake\" class=\"wp-image-17250 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130648\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-lake.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130648\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-lake-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130648\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-lake-600x404.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130648\/things-to-do-kandy-sri-lanka-lake-450x303.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltino